{"tid":1428503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十分可疑！！「汽油彈」與「燃燒彈」","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:22.000Z","uid":39808,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9750313b1cf69ce37c9190dddcd4d7c68d8b6f2e","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"先說明一下兩個名詞<br />\n<strong>汽油彈</strong><br />\n<em>用玻璃樽作容器嘅一般氣油彈</em><br />\n<strong>燃燒彈</strong><br />\n1 <em>汽油彈嘅另一稱謂</em><br />\n2 <em>軍事上禁用嘅白磷彈嗰類軍用武器，在這時局下，並不存在軍用武器燃燒彈</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汽油彈同燃燒彈可以理解為同一種物品，但何以警方、消防，以至港澳辦，都將汽油彈與燃燒彈當作兩類不同物品看待呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n我認為將汽油彈與燃燒彈當作兩類不同物品看待，這個統一口徑，並非由下而上，從調查&quot;證物&quot;而來，因為即使警方在此不具備足夠專業知識，消防理應了解汽油彈與燃燒彈為同一種物品，不應該出現此等言論。故<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">這統一口徑的出處，很有可能是由上而下的劇本，劇本撰寫人應是警方與消防以上的人。我懷疑，策劃者可能制定了兩種成分不同的汽油彈，分別稱為&quot;汽油彈&quot;與&quot;燃燒彈&quot;，更可能已經製作了，當作了&quot;證物&quot;，甚至實際地當作武器使用了</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><ins><strong>有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華</strong></ins>交代天水圍拘捕行動，表示早前接獲線報，顯示天水圍天瑞邨一單位內有人製作武器。昨晚警方帶同搜查令入屋，檢獲30個用乒乓球製的煙霧彈和50萬元現金等；並拘捕2女1男，年齡介乎23至47歲。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華表示，上述兩宗案件和近日一連串的暴力示威活動有關。他表示，在元朗及中上環遊行現場，均發現示威者使用的<span style=\"color: red;\">汽油彈</span>、鋼鐵彈珠和<span style=\"color: gold;\">燃燒彈</span>，形容是可致命的武器。警方亦展示網上討論區連登及通訊軟件 Telegram 的對話圖片，指有網民鼓吹用仿製槍械及強力激光槍對付警員。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066206&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=32af998f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066206&h=29cae254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066206</a><br />\n<br />\n  政務司司長張建宗及保安局局長李家超今日（八月六日）就不合作運動的有關影響舉行記者會。路政署副署長吳偉強、運輸署助理署長（管理及輔助客運）郭惠英和<strong><ins>消防處副消防總長（質素保證及管理）鄭瑞安</ins></strong>亦有出席。以下是鄭瑞安的開場發言： <br />\n<br />\n​  各位：<br />\n<br />\n  昨日香港不同地區出現多宗遊行示威及聚眾集會，其間示威人士以突襲形式佔據道路，令香港多處主要幹道同一時間嚴重堵塞，對本處提供的緊急服務構成了嚴重的影響。<br />\n<br />\n  昨日有示威人士於集會期間，投擲<span style=\"color: red;\">汽油彈</span>及<span style=\"color: gold;\">燃燒彈</span>，更在不同地點包括街道、警署和其他建築物縱火，縱火的規模亦越來越大，焚燒的雜物亦越來越多。昨日，本處一共處理了21宗縱火事故。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-06<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/06/P2019080600696.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F06%2FP2019080600696.htm&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=d5d7243b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/06/P2019080600696.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n  <strong><ins>杨光</ins></strong>说，近两个月来，在香港发生的示威游行活动完全超出集会、游行、示威自由的范畴，已演化为极端暴力行为，手段不断翻新、烈度不断升级、破坏性不断加剧，令人触目惊心。一小部分激进示威者以警察为袭击目标，使用的工具从砖头、铁枝发展到烟雾弹、<span style=\"color: red;\">汽油弹</span>、弓箭等致命武器，并实施纵火，还有人在网上公然鼓吹使用致命手法袭击警察。这些行为对香港警务人员和广大市民的生命财产安全造成严重伤害。已有461人在暴力冲突中受伤，其中包括139名警务人员。<br />\n<br />\n  他指出，更令人愤慨和需要高度警觉的是，部分激进分子撕毁香港基本法，污损国徽。8月3日傍晚，几名无耻之徒在尖沙咀拆下某建筑物前悬挂的中华人民共和国国旗，扔入海中。这一行径严重触犯法律，公然冒犯国家尊严，挑战&ldquo;一国两制&rdquo;原则底线。5日，反对派发动罢工，造成约250次航班被取消，观塘等8条地铁线停止服务超过5小时，红磡隧道和数条交通干线受阻。极端暴力分子向警署投掷<span style=\"color: gold;\">燃烧弹</span>，在多处纵火。当晚7点多，极端激进分子再次到尖沙咀扯下国旗，扔入海中。这些暴徒可谓嚣张至极、丧心病狂。未来等待他们的将是法律之剑的重击，是耻辱柱上抹不掉的刻痕。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-06<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinanews.com/ga/2019/08-06/8918856.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinanews.com%2Fga%2F2019%2F08-06%2F8918856.shtml&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a68e3f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinanews.com/ga/2019/08-06/8918856.shtml</a></span>"},{"pid":"9f4281e23b37ee91eeae0400dbe5eb6297d45956","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4400b543e2a15a1fa97e5b9fb7d295017256278e","tid":1428503,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e35337a24637b31c2ab52a12848ab8ec1ceeb02","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"雖然無實質證據，但真係極之可疑"},{"pid":"e594bc266f21a3718f9fdbd072cf1fd75f4b67fa","tid":1428503,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"汽油=/=火水=/=柴油"},{"pid":"c89997829e1856da69595e5853dfb22f601438f3","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e594bc266f21a3718f9fdbd072cf1fd75f4b67fa","tid":1428503,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"汽油=/=火水=/=柴油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"從來汽油彈都無指定用汽油，汽油彈只係泛稱"},{"pid":"9b984350acbe1bb90f6a9394e1a297b0e0826c18","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3310869783c9e2cdcb5a76271e980daad2d40d1","tid":1428503,"uid":151507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:26:38.000Z","msg":"不合作運動&mdash; 每週罷買日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422644</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTg討論：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FHWE6g9ZNIROYtOqBJ8Ecw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFHWE6g9ZNIROYtOqBJ8Ecw&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=dac3cc8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FHWE6g9ZNIROYtOqBJ8Ecw</a><br />\n<br />\n開左投票post決定罷買日數 請幫推/廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1427436/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1427436/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9583205d1e1a91465254e572af5ddf398019f73f","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bc2b4ccaea23a61f5280ad48f28927f4e00ca4f","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c89997829e1856da69595e5853dfb22f601438f3","tid":1428503,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e594bc266f21a3718f9fdbd072cf1fd75f4b67fa","tid":1428503,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"汽油=/=火水=/=柴油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"從來汽油彈都無指定用汽油，汽油彈只係泛稱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"唔好話用汽油算汽油彈，用其他算燃燒彈，就算佢要咁樣分，佢點分出來，除非佢自己製作嘅就好易分"},{"pid":"c278619aad42203fb2c01cf7642e2d4bbca4ce65","tid":1428503,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas"}]}